%^BOLD%^-=%^CYAN%^Magic Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

A caster who draws upon the magic domain is granted
special power from the Weave.  This power may allow
him to avoid being fooled by illusion or to break
even powerful curses.

Clerics with the Magic Domain gain the following benefits:
- %^BOLD%^CYAN%^Dispelling Touch%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The magic domain contains the following spells:

Color Spray, Resist Energy, Break Curse, Freedom of Movement, Mystic Bolt, Protection from spells, True Seeing, Spellscar, Clashing Rocks

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Kismet

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
